00:14:26.190 --> 00:14:27.900
And so, if you're the king,

00:14:27.900 --> 00:14:31.470
you need to counterbalance
the force of these magnates,

00:14:31.470 --> 00:14:32.303
of these great nobles.

00:14:32.303 --> 00:14:33.136
And so what do you do?

00:14:33.136 --> 00:14:37.080
Again, you give rights to
the nobility as a whole.

00:14:37.080 --> 00:14:38.790
You try to bring the lesser nobility,

00:14:38.790 --> 00:14:40.680
the middle nobility over to your side.

00:14:40.680 --> 00:14:44.700
And so in order to do
that, you give them rights.

00:14:44.700 --> 00:14:47.490
So some of these rights as
